{"tid":2331120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（個案編號：7379）伊利沙伯醫院一名63歲確診患者逃離醫院　院方報警求助","createTime":"2020-12-18T13:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:52:05.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"21796fcc00f972b8213e79a768983a04f8d5aa87","tid":2331120,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】伊利沙伯醫院表示，一名63歲確診新冠毒病的男病人（個案編號：7379），由12月14日起入住隔離病房接受治療，在今日（12月18日）下午約五時，病房職員發現病人試圖離開病房，職員隨即追出，但病人已經樓梯逃去無蹤。病房職員立即通知醫院保安在院內進行搜索，但未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n院方報警求助，並會全力配合警方的調查。醫院亦已向衞生防護中心通報有關事件，並已透過早期事故通報系統向醫院管理局總辦事處匯報事件。<br />\n<br />\n病人身高約1.6米，中等身材及蓄黑色短頭髮，離院時身穿病人服、深藍色外套及運動鞋，並有佩戴外科口罩。院方呼籲市民若發現有關病人，請通知警方或致電本院熱線電話3506 8944。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=19908&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D19908%26refer%3DShare&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=2d874d7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D19908%26refer%3DShare&h=f3aa3906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=19908&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"5b32a62e584e7f3dd7433f4fc2d2933d0777bb19","tid":2331120,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a503d6fedae4d79dc5cade31696aa27ab05b6776","tid":2331120,"uid":12171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmWUYKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmWUYKy.jpg&h=cc95898c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3cfd4219bdc2f59ee78fa1240447b733ebeb201","tid":2331120,"uid":37505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b32a62e584e7f3dd7433f4fc2d2933d0777bb19","tid":2331120,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit